text:
Two questions I have my students ask about every question. 
1. What makes this question hard?
2. What is one thing I can do that would make it easier

Breaking down complex math into single steps eliminates so much stress for those that get easily  overwhelmed in math
#iteachmath

Is odd
Has an even # in tens place
Is composite
Is a multiple of 10
Is not a multiple of 5
